thread.title: GIBBS PATRICIA

author: GIBBS PATRICIA
title: GIBBS PATRICIA
text: Brilliant service and exact car. No satnav available but we enjoyed using a paper map which was great way to explore! They do have satnavs but had run out of them when we picked up car, so if you want one then maybe pre book. Didn't bother us though. Staff helpful and car was great value and nice and clean. Definately would book again with rentalcars. Thankyou.
